headline: Cognizant Named to Forbes' list of Canada's Best Employers for Company Culture 2025
summary: Cognizant (NASDAQ: CTSH) is proud to be named to Forbes' inaugural list of Canada's Best Employers for Company Culture 2025. This prestigious recognition is presented by Forbes and Statista, the world-leading statistics portal and industry ranking provider.
